    "MSRA [56] In the entity classifications of location name, institution name, and person name, the MSRA dataset on Chinese NER from Microsoft Research Asia (MSRA) is made up approximately 50,000 Chinese entity recognition annotations.THE GENIA [56] THE GENIA dataset has been taken from the biomedical literature, which helps with bio-text mining system development."
